---
title: Caribbean Jerk Pumpkin & Black Bean Salad with Feta & Shredded Coconut
description: Turn a vegetarian salad into a hearty flavour explosion with this medley of gently spiced pumpkin, black beans and fresh greens. It’s a satisfying taste of Jamaica in a veggie-loaded and colourful bowl.
